		"description": "<p>At 20th level, you gain the following abilities:</p>\n<h2>Frenzied Finisher</h2>\n<p>When you drop a foe to 0 hit points as per your @UUID[Compendium.a5e-bloody-heretics.bloody-heretics.Item.DhH2HdUvPQYNIbWE]{Accelerated Recovery} feature, you instead regain a number of hit points equal to that creature&rsquo;s CR, and the number of hit dice you recover is equal to twice your Constitution modifier.</p>\n<p>Additionally, while under the effects of your @UUID[Compendium.a5e-bloody-heretics.bloody-heretics.Item.eSbauOXs2C1ajtDf]{Blood Frenzy}, when you would hit with a weapon attack you may choose to turn the hit into a critical hit. Once you have used this ability to alter a strike in this fashion, you may not use it again until you complete a short or a long rest.</p>\n<h2>Remember Thyself</h2>\n<p>When you would unwillingly fail your Wisdom saving throw to resist your @UUID[Compendium.a5e-bloody-heretics.bloody-heretics.Item.eSbauOXs2C1ajtDf]{Blood Frenzy}, you may choose to succeed instead. Once you have resisted the Frenzy in this way, you may not do so again until you complete a short or a long rest.</p>",
